    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and stir in your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong>, <strong>dried basil </strong>and<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong></p><p>Add<strong> half </strong>of<strong> </strong>your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> (save the rest for later!) – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
