    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cauliflower has been roasting for 30 min, remove the dish[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>from the oven and pour the<strong> tomato sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Top with the<strong> torn mozzarella </strong>and sprinkle over your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Return the dish[es] to the oven for 20 min further or until the cheese has melted and everything's bubbling and tender – this is your<strong> baked cheesy cauliflower parmigiana</strong></p>",
