    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cauliflower parmigiana is almost done, add your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
