      "instruction": "<p>To serve, tear your <strong>basil leaves</strong> over the<strong> baked cheesy cauliflower parmigiana</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> baby leaf salad </strong>with <strong>olive oil</strong> and the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar</strong></p><p>Serve everything with the <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> to the side for scooping</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
